      },
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "I'm sure you know this and all, but I'll still ask just in case. Which of these monsters will you not be seeing at the #m10007000#? \\n\\n#L0##b#o41##l\\n#L1##o44##l\\n#L2##o46##l"
