      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Did you collect them all? If the ingredients aren't fresh, I may not pay you for your service. Of course, you also need to have enough ingredients. Now, let's see..."
